plot: The women gather at Vicki's for a post Bali dinner party and with leftover tensions from the trip still running high, the ladies lay everything on the table. Tamra comes face-to-face with Brooks, and an apology from Shannon's husband David sparks an unexpected fight. Meanwhile, Vicki's daughter Briana and Tamra's son Ryan officially say goodbye to the OC, leaving their mothers in tears.—Anonymous
